Header: When dives go wrong, mishaps from last year’s Cliff Diving World Series
Content: With the new season of the Red Bull Cliff Diving World Series about to start here’s a reminder of what can go wrong.While the bravery and skill of the competitors is not in doubt, last year’s events proved that even the best divers, such as champion Gary Hunt, can sometimes get it wrong. The 2019 championship starts in the Philippines on April 13.
